Test passed by RealtimeClusterIntegrationTest.

I manually adding condition:
if (_segment instanceof RealtimeSegment) {
    baseFilterOperator = new ScanBasedFilterOperator(ds, startDocId, endDocId);
} before:  https://github.com/linkedin/pinot/blob/master/pinot-core/src/main/java/com/linkedin/pinot/core/plan/FilterPlanNode.java#L118

So all the filtering query will use ScanBasedFilterOperator, not BitmapBasedFilterOperator.

RealtimeClusterIntegrationTest failed before this patch.
